Albums featuring Claudio Abbado include "Claudio Abbado Conducts Tchaikovsky," "Symphonies Nos. 2 & 4," and "Symphonies 4 & 5." Claudio Abbado has worked with various orchestras, including the London Symphony Orchestra and the Chicago Symphony Orchestra. Significant recordings include "Pictures at an Exhibition," "Symphony No. 9," and "Symphony No. 6 'Pathetique.'"
Claudio Abbado.music.artist.genre: Claudio Abbado is associated with Classical music and Opera.
Claudio Abbado.music.artist.label: Claudio Abbado has been associated with labels such as CBS, Decca Records, Deutsche Grammophon, EMI, Nuova Era, Philips Records, PolyGram, RCA Records, and Sony Records.
